    <criterion testable="true">No production code modified in `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/` (verified via `git diff src/server/api/`).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Memo at `notes/test-infra-bff-cascading-fix-2026-05-26.md` catalogs all 69 errors + fixes.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    This task exists because task 069 surfaced these errors. They were all pre-existing — none
    introduced by R4. The work is mostly mechanical (apply bulk patterns) but volume-intensive
    (~17 files, ~69 errors). Estimated 12-16h.

    Bulk pattern for CS7036 logger drift:
    ```csharp
    // Before (compile error)
    var sut = new EmailAnalysisJobHandler(deps...);

    // After (added ILogger<T> param)
    var sut = new EmailAnalysisJobHandler(deps..., NullLogger<EmailAnalysisJobHandler>.Instance);
    ```

    DO NOT pursue (out of scope): test quality improvements, framework migration, coverage expansion.
    Narrow goal: build green + suite running.

    R4 acceptance criteria depending on this: 050/053/054 tests must execute as part of CI gate.
  </notes>

